{
  "stem": "16245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I do remember unloading railway trucks, wheat from railway trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's about all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We weren't there very long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At night, I do remember meeting a lot of people who we knew, among others-- for instance, my headmaster, as well as teachers from our school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just about everybody was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, none I remember there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one thing that sticks in my memory that, when the Russians were so close that we could see Russian things, all of a sudden gendarmes came out of nowhere and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] told us to assemble and take us, they were going to take us elsewhere.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these gendarmes had a bad reputation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were responsible for all the deportation of Jews to Auschwitz, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were-- it was one night, they got us, got us marching in sort of rough units.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the one incident I remember was that they wouldn't carry their own ammunition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had Tommy guns and a kind of a round box full of ammunition, which was damn heavy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had our own rucksacks to carry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they gave their ammunition box to the nearest Jew in the formation, who was handing it over after the-- after a while to the next one, until it came to me, and I threw the damn thing away.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I must have been either stupid or a hero.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And nothing ever came of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were looking for it, they couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were in a hurry to get to the other side of the Danube because, obviously, they felt that the Russians wouldn't stop.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, I can't remember if I would have told anybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I probably didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
